Card - Class in model.card
This class describes a Card object, it has a suit and a rank to describe a playing card.
Card(Card.Rank, Card.Suit) - Constructor for class model.card.Card
Card constructor accepts a Rank and a Suit and stores them in the rank and suit instance variables when the card is created.
Card.CardComparator - Class in model.card
Compares c1 and c2 solely by rank.
